      <h1>Publicity and Media</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="slab-bordered">
      <div class="section-9-3-2-col">
        <div class="col-left">
          <h2 class="h2_h3"><a name="publicity"></a>Contacting the University of Chicago Press Publicity Department</h2>

<p><span class="contact_name">The University of Chicago Press<br />
Publicity Department</span><br />
1427 East 60th Street<br />
Chicago, Illinois 60637 USA<br />
<span class="contact_method">Voice:</span> <a href="tel:+17737027740">(773) 702-7740</a><br />
<span class="contact_method">Fax:</span> <a href="tel:+17737029756">(773) 702-9756</a><br />
<span class="contact_method">E-mail:</span> <a class="contact_email" href="mailto:press_publicity@uchicago.edu">press_publicity@uchicago.edu</a></p>

<h2><a name="reviewrequest"></a>Requesting a Review Copy</h2>

<p>To request a review copy, you may contact us by e-mail at <a class="contact_email" href="mailto:press_publicity@uchicago.edu">press_publicity@uchicago.edu</a>, by phone at (773) 702-7740, or fax at (773) 702-9756. Please be sure to include the title and author of the book, the title of your publication, your name, and full mailing address.</p>

<h2><a name="catalogs"></a>Catalogs</h2>

<p>Our recent seasonal catalogs are <a href="/books/catalogs.html">available in PDF format</a>.</p>

        </div>
        <div class="col-right"></div>
      </div>
